WEBVTT

00:01.602 --> 00:02.370
Everybody Hates Chris #026
"Everybody Hates a Liar"
Closed Captioned

00:02.403 --> 00:03.637
(Berlin's "No More Words"
playing)

00:03.671 --> 00:06.340
CHRIS ROCK:
Tasha Clarkson was the new
girl next door.

00:06.374 --> 00:08.542
Unlike just about every other
girl in the neighborhood,

00:08.576 --> 00:09.743
she didn't hate me.

00:09.777 --> 00:10.744
Hi, Chris.
Hey, Tasha.

00:10.778 --> 00:13.547
I always tried to play it
cool around her,

00:13.581 --> 00:15.249
but every time she came
out the door,

00:15.283 --> 00:16.517
it looked like this...

00:20.821 --> 00:23.091
But Tasha's grandmother was one
of the strictest parents

00:23.124 --> 00:24.625
on the block.

00:24.658 --> 00:27.561
Where you going
dressed like that?

00:27.595 --> 00:30.098
Grandma, I have on
everything but gloves.

00:30.131 --> 00:31.599
Put some gloves on.

00:32.733 --> 00:34.635
Showing your hands to people.

00:34.668 --> 00:36.770
And it was 79 degrees.

00:36.804 --> 00:38.739
So I figured the smartest
thing to do

00:38.772 --> 00:41.175
was to just leave Tasha alone.

00:43.811 --> 00:45.646
Chris, come quick. I need you.

00:45.679 --> 00:47.715
So much for that plan.

00:49.250 --> 00:51.752
Do you see it?!
Chris, do you see it?!

00:51.785 --> 00:53.787
Oh, yeah, I see it.

00:53.821 --> 00:56.657
But what do you want
me to do with it?

00:59.260 --> 01:01.329
Get it out!

01:01.362 --> 01:03.764
Get it out of my closet!
Okay, okay, okay.
Stop screaming please.

01:03.797 --> 01:05.299
Stop, stop...

01:05.333 --> 01:07.368
She's screaming like
the mouse had a gun.

01:21.215 --> 01:22.416
Thank you.

01:22.450 --> 01:24.418
No problem.

01:24.452 --> 01:27.255
To you, that just looked
like a kiss on the cheek,

01:27.288 --> 01:29.657
but to me it felt
like this...

01:34.495 --> 01:36.664
Yo.

01:36.697 --> 01:38.566
Little dude from
across the street.

01:38.599 --> 01:41.269
Come here.

01:41.302 --> 01:43.671
Listen, man, I don't
have any money.

01:43.704 --> 01:45.206
I don't want your money,
little dude.

01:45.239 --> 01:46.840
I want to know how
you got Tasha.

01:46.874 --> 01:48.609
Got Tasha what?

01:48.642 --> 01:50.878
Come on, little dude.
I saw that.

01:50.911 --> 01:53.714
Every little dude on the block
been trying to get next to her.

01:53.747 --> 01:55.683
Little dude from up
on the third floor,

01:55.716 --> 01:57.518
little dude from
around the corner,

01:57.551 --> 01:59.520
little dude with
the funny leg,

01:59.553 --> 02:01.522
little dude with
the little loft,

02:01.555 --> 02:04.558
little dude that be
with big dude... and Kenny.

02:04.592 --> 02:06.527
Now I know why
they can't get nowhere.

02:06.560 --> 02:09.863
'Cause little dude from across
the street is on the case.

02:09.897 --> 02:11.565
Now why you ain't
tell nobody?

02:11.599 --> 02:12.733
Hey, well, you know.

02:12.766 --> 02:14.702
That's what you said when you
didn't want to lie,

02:14.735 --> 02:15.936
but you didn't want
to tell the truth.

02:15.969 --> 02:18.306
I underestimated
you, little dude.

02:18.339 --> 02:19.773
I ain't think you
had it in you.

02:19.807 --> 02:22.643
Tasha. Mean as her
grandmom is.

02:22.676 --> 02:25.246
You a bad man,
little dude.

02:25.279 --> 02:26.447
Just do me a favor.

02:26.480 --> 02:27.615
Don't tell anybody?

02:27.648 --> 02:29.483
It's between me and you.

02:29.517 --> 02:32.220
:
Little dude from
across the street.

02:32.253 --> 02:33.721
Mackin'.

02:33.754 --> 02:36.290
I should have told him the
truth that nothing happened,

02:36.324 --> 02:37.925
but, hey, well, you know.

02:46.267 --> 02:47.968
* Oh... make it funky now!

02:48.001 --> 02:51.972
